code: @Override public void collect(StreamRecord<OUT> record) {     Set<Output<StreamRecord<OUT>>> selectedOutputs = selectOutputs(record).     if (selectedOutputs.isEmpty()) {         return.     }     Iterator<Output<StreamRecord<OUT>>> it = selectedOutputs.iterator().     while (true) {         Output<StreamRecord<OUT>> out = it.next().         if (it.hasNext()) {             // we don't have the last output             // perform a shallow copy             StreamRecord<OUT> shallowCopy = record.copy(record.getValue()).             out.collect(shallowCopy).         } else {             // this is the last output             out.collect(record).             break.         }     } }
